    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/0ffa4bc4472b824e2b709f36b0c0bde6.poster.avif?t=1729660095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/0ffa4bc4472b824e2b709f36b0c0bde6.webm?t=1729660095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/0ffa4bc4472b824e2b709f36b0c0bde6.mp4?t=1729660095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >您需要击败越来越强大的杠铃BOSS！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备深蹲！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少年的深蹲恐惧化为了怪物！帮助少年一步步成长，迎接新的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无条件深蹲》准备了12种独特的杠铃！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要少年坚持锻炼，不论速度多慢，杠铃都会朝终点移动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*在体验版中，您最多可以挑战4个阶段的BOSS。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/88032e0134830a7640094a80d1bf61bc.poster.avif?t=1729660095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/88032e0134830a7640094a80d1bf61bc.webm?t=1729660095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/88032e0134830a7640094a80d1bf61bc.mp4?t=1729660095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验在健身房和学校里发生的各种有趣和离奇的故事！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >健身房总是充满金属的碰撞声和汗水的气味，而学校则总是充满朋友们的喧闹声。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据您的选择，少年会与周围的人互动并逐渐成长！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《无条件深蹲》中，您可以体验超过20个独立故事，遇到30多个NPC角色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在健身房中体验各种搞笑和荒诞的事件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证少年如何在学校里面对并克服欺凌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*I体验版中只能体验前4个阶段的故事内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/5fda40b8274cfc955b2e95a6b9cc4cff.poster.avif?t=1729660095\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/5fda40b8274cfc955b2e95a6b9cc4cff.webm?t=1729660095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3149080/extras/5fda40b8274cfc955b2e95a6b9cc4cff.mp4?t=1729660095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无条件深蹲》是一款结合视觉小说和弹幕动作的射击游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对拥有各种弹幕攻击模式的杠铃BOSS，完成深蹲挑战并将杠铃推向顶端！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受专属于您的故事！在《无条件深蹲》中，故事会根据您的选择产生分支，推动剧情发展！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着少年的成长，他将解锁新的天赋！使用更强大、更独特的能力挑战杠铃！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您还可以自定义喜爱的训练项目！根据您的选择，BOSS的攻击模式也会有所变化！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满汗水与力量的健身房中，遇见各种奇人异事，帮助少年成长！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与少年一起在学校中面对恶友的不公和欺凌！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*体验版中，天赋觉醒限制在前6个阶段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*体验版中，辅助训练只会以最简单的难度出现。</p>",
